Excellent dish - it was easy to make, and it is definately a 'comfort food!' The sauce is VERY rich, however, so be warned!

Rating: 4
My favorite part of the chicken is the dark meat and this recipe really does it justice. The previous reviewer is correct in suggesting a longer cooking time. I used fresh small onions instead of the frozen and also would suggest putting the potatoes in the pan when you add the chicken back in. I hated to add the creme fraiche, but it really did make the sauce. I can't wait to see the suggestions of other cooks on how to keep the flavor without using this ingredient, perhaps some no fat sour cream? Great flavors in this recipe.

